{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Inspired by classic fighting\u00a0games from the 90's such as Street Fighter, Fatal Fury and The King of Fighters, 'Pocket Bravery' channels the 'Neo Geo Pocket' aesthetic for a modern\u00a0fighting game with a retro twist!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1555150/extras/combo.gif?t=1737475365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With original characters, vibrant colours and an impressive combat system, 'Pocket Bravery'\u00a0is\u00a0designed with\u00a0high-level players in mind, while making it easily accessible for beginners to pick-up-and-play! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1555150/extras/Nuno_Special_Attack_2.gif?t=1737475365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Choose Your Fighter! </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Select from a diverse 12 character roster, each with their own unique\u00a0abilities and play styles! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1555150/extras/character_select.gif?t=1737475365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Local and Online Multiplayer\u00a0with 'Rollback Netcode </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clash head-to-head worldwide with ultra-low latency rollback code in online multiplayer or take on your friends locally! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1555150/extras/Daisuke_elemental_2.gif?t=1737475365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Master An Elemental-Based Combat System </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Channel your inner 'Ichor', a unique elemental energy blessing each one of the playable characters in Pocket Bravery. Master the elements to open up new  offensive or defensive possibilities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1555150/extras/ELEMENTAL.gif?t=1737475365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unleash Screen-Filling Ultimate Attacks!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Charge up to unleash your ultimate attack!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1555150/extras/Kimberly_s_special_elemental.gif?t=1737475365\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Be brave","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1555150/13449c5076159e81e4b1de12c8fd7441f533a7c5.jpg"},{"name":"Show me who you really are","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1555150/20af081584786225a96325f2f6a61cfd09eccdac.jpg"},{"name":"Avatar ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1555150/cc79aa3b842277cba4d7039812b625762f2cfd61.jpg"},{"name":"Treta Moment","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1555150/5cd06f401a0fa13b9b64f357ef99311f076dcee3.jpg"},{"name":"Predictable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1555150/e3593d3e4b0b54dca6d02ac2ec56856429e10937.jpg"},{"name":"Enter the Matrix","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1555150/b609a958f075d850a8a23439e894351fdd5c57d5.jpg"},{"name":"Perfectionist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1555150/8e1c990e88ecf6084a2acc5dd54363094fe8a4b8.jpg"},{"name":"Until the last breath","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1555150/c888cdf5cbd72a4c13aa27734adcc3d9e8c37ece.jpg"},{"name":"\"Button Masher\"","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/